Synthetic construct has been made based on Dengue virus type 1 (strain Nauru/West Pac/1974) by Centre for Medicines Discovery, University of Oxford, and the assay has been performed by Weizmann Institute of Science.The protocol is publicly available: dx.doi.org/10.17504/protocols.io.q26g7yebkgwz/v3
